(1, 1, '2330618_2616816.jpg', 'Timothy Cooper', 'Blueprint Screenwriting Group', '<p>Timothy Cooper is a filmmaker, playwright, comedy writer, and teacher.&nbsp;He&nbsp;has taught hundreds of writers throughout the country about screenwriting, storytelling, improv comedy, and writing. He founded Blueprint Screenwriting Group in the spring of 2014 to teach screenwriting in a small, constructive, creative writing-group environment.</p>', 'New York', 12, NULL, '<p>Timothy Cooper is a filmmaker, playwright, comedy writer, and teacher based in Brooklyn, New York.<br /><br />He wrote and directed the web sitcom, Concierge, the Series,&nbsp;&nbsp;starring comedians from&nbsp;<em>Saturday Night Live, 30 Rock</em>,<em>&nbsp;Bridesmaids</em>,<em>&nbsp;Last Comic Standing</em>, the Onion News Network, CollegeHumor, and Upright Citizens Brigade. For his work on&nbsp;<em>Concierge</em>, he was nominated for a Writers Guild Award&nbsp;for Outstanding Achievement in Writing Original New Media. The series was also an official selection of the&nbsp;International Television Festival&nbsp;and the&nbsp;Screen Actors Guild Foundation Short Film Showcase.<br /><br />His debut political comedy video, &ldquo;Transparency,&rdquo; was featured on the front pages of YouTube Comedy and Slate magazine. He also directed two shows that played at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre in New York City: the improvised play&nbsp;<em>Sunny-Side Up</em>, and&nbsp;<em>Farebeater: Improv in a Cab</em>, both starring cast members from&nbsp;<em>Silicon Valley</em>,&nbsp;<em>The League</em>,&nbsp;<em>Conan</em>, and more.<br /><br />Timothy''s first feature-writing credit,&nbsp;<em>Away from Here</em>, starring Nick Stahl, Alicia Witt, and Ray Wise, is available on Amazon.<br /><br />He also wrote and directed the two-screen digital sitcom pilot&nbsp;<em>We Are Criminal Masterminds</em>, which was a top-five nationwide finalist in the Samsung Second Screen Storytellers Competition at the New York Television Festival. &nbsp;Timothy is also the creator of 365&nbsp;log lines, where he posted an original movie idea every day for a year.<br /><br />He''s written commercials for dozens of high-profile brands&nbsp;to promote the YouTube brand during the 2014 Super Bowl. He was a contributing joke writer for host Colin Quinn at the 2014 Writers Guild Awards, and again for host Larry Wilmore at the 2015 Writers Guild Awards.<br /><br />Timothy is currently developing multiple pilots and features with a variety of production companies.</p>', '{"0":"Script Coverage","1":"Script Consultant","2":"Development Notes","3":" Script Writing","4":"Ghost Writing","5":"Rewrite Assistance","6":"Proofreading & Script Formatting","7":"Phone Consultation","other":["Other "]}', '["WGA Member","Script Consultant","Script Reader","Script Writer","Director","Producer"]', 'website', 'twiter', 'Facebook', 'sd', 'twiter', 'graduated', 'no-experience', 'hindi, maghi', NULL, NULL, 'Chrysanthemum.jpg', '1', 'indain film fair, Kans ', 0, '2016-04-23 11:46:03', '2014-05-21 11:08:08'),
